[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      333[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // If embedding fails, we cannot run kNN at all.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      334[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         // Fall back to primary model only; flag the gap.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      335[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         primary_score = invoke_xgboost(claim_features)
